# config/package-lists/desktop-firefox.list.chroot
# Firefox ESR with school-safe enterprise policy.
# Policy file shipped at: config/includes.chroot/etc/firefox-esr/policies/policies.json
#
# En-GB UI; Hindi/Marathi langpacks are Firefox addons (not Debian packages —
# firefox-esr-l10n-hi doesn't exist in trixie). Telemetry/studies/Pocket
# disabled, camera/mic/location blocked, SafeBrowsing always on,
# ManagedBookmarks pin to learning portals.

firefox-esr
firefox-esr-l10n-en-gb
